commit.title: [gitlab] [ci] Quick & Dirty job to test with OCaml trunk.
commit.message:
[gitlab] [ci] Quick & Dirty job to test with OCaml trunk.

We build without Camlp5, using an older switch to create the
pre-processed files. This should be improved.

Note that for some reason the 4.08 switch is not yet available in OPAM
2.
